<view class='bg-gradual-blue padding radius text-center shadow-blur title_css page'>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-red light solid-bottom margin-top action" hidden="{{hidden_or_not}}">
    <view class="flex padding justify-between">
      <text class='text-red'></text>更新说明（点击右侧关闭）
    </view>
    <view class="flex padding justify-between">
      <button class="cu-btn lines-red round shadow sm" bindtap="close_it">
        <view class="icon-close text-red"></view>
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last' hidden="{{hidden_or_not}}">
    <view class='text-sm'>v3.0.0（2019.08.22）</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>1. 增加了“法语背单词”功能，目前的词库为“法语5000词频”，涵盖大部分常用法语单词。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>2. 修改了设置页面，“法语背单词”和“法语动词变位”分开设置。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>3. 修改了云同步方式。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>4. 修改了部分界面。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>5. 修复了强化练习时态设置的错误。</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>6. 修改了小程序的名称：法语记忆 学背单词动词变位</view>
    <view class='text-sm'>具体内容请参见 https://uniquelab.cn/conj-helper-3-0-0</view>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow sm' bindtap="copy_current">点击复制网址</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-mauve light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-mauve'></text>关于法语记忆：学背单词动词变位
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="help">📄使用帮助</button>
        <button class='cu-btn lines-blue round shadow' open-type="feedback">❌报错和建议</button>
      </view>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="like_me">✨赞赏支持我</button>
        <button class='cu-btn lines-blue round shadow' bindtap="copy">😻小程序主页</button>
      </view>
      <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>若使用过程中，有疑问、bug、错误、显示为null的情况、改进意见，欢迎点击报错和建议进行反馈，反馈时注明具体单词方便改正哦。</view>
      <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>小程序原名：法语动词变位记忆小助手</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-red light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-red'></text>设置
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="settings_vocab">背单词设置</button>
      </view>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-blue round shadow' bindtap="settings_conj">动词变位设置</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-grey light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-grey'></text>同步设置
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <!-- 用户 openid style="background-image: url({{avatarUrl}})" -->
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button open-type="getUserInfo" bindgetuserinfo="onGetUserInfo" class="cu-btn lines-red round shadow" bindtap="onGetOpenid_upload">⬆本地上传</button>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button open-type="getUserInfo" bindgetuserinfo="onGetUserInfo" class="cu-btn lines-blue round shadow" bindtap="onGetOpenid_download">⬇云端下载</button>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='text-left text-xs text-grey padding'>点击上方登陆，登陆之后可以同步。“本地上传”将覆盖云端数据；“云端下载”将覆盖本地数据</view>
  </view>

  <view class="cu-bar bg-red light solid-bottom margin-top">
    <view class='action'>
      <text class='icon-title text-red'></text>小程序推荐
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class='padding bg-white bg-white-last'>
    <view class='box'>
      <view class="cu-bar btn-group">
        <button class='cu-btn bg-red round shadow' bindtap="hard_choice">艰难的选择</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

</view>